metadata.description: A community-driven ecosystem built on the CheetahWorld metaverse. CheetahWorld launches within a state of anarchy that unravels into a PVE tournament game for a 69 $ETH prize. Cheetah's come in a range of colors + traits with a collection size of 3,333. Each Cheetah serves as the genesis point of the CheetahWorld ecosystem. Allowing owners to help create the CheetahWorld metaverse and vote for further innovations and experiences paid for by the CheetahWorld Treasury
metadata.name: CheetahWorld #1
